        "description": "I downloaded the binary tarball to play with hadoop 2.8.0 and noticed that the size has almost doubled. The unpacked tarball is multiple GB big:\n\n{code}\n$ du -sh hadoop-2.8.0\n2.2G\thadoop-2.8.0\n{code}\n\nThe latest hadoop 2.7.x is only 332MB upacked:\n\n{code}\n$ du -sh hadoop-2.7.3\n332M\thadoop-2.7.3\n{code}\n\nThe size increase seems to be in share/doc/\n\n{code}\n$ du -sh hadoop-2.8.0/share/doc/\n2.0G\thadoop-2.8.0/share/doc/\n{code}\n\n{code}\n$ du -sh hadoop-2.7.3/share/doc/\n 94M\thadoop-2.7.3/share/doc/\n{code}\n\nIt looks like something went wrong during the build.",
